songs.title: Fuckin’ With D

C'mon!

Than you and him can discuss what I did, yeah it was

Now, you hear my shit all on the street i'm kinda hot

These is tha niggas that

I ain't gonna stoppa', cocka, unlocka, let 'em go, give it to his man just to let him know

Got what was yourz and tried to steal sometin' wit it, now
(Feel sometin' hit it)
Your chest that is, the best that is, is probaly the best that slid, yo stress that kid!
